In view of the foregoing, we recommend the following:

a. Require the Deputized MDDRMO to submit the Report on the Sources and Utilization of the LDRRMF duly certified by the Provincial Accountant, through LDRRMC and LDC, to the COA on or before the 15th day after the end of each month to facilitate the timely monitoring of implementation of LDRRMPs and balance of fund, if there is any, by the concerned offices, copy furnished Office of the Civil Defense and the Local Government Operation Officer of the Department of Interior and Local Government;

b. Require the Secretariat of the MDRRMC to post the Report and Utilization of LDRRMF in the agency website and in conspicuous places within the Municipality and other areas where the public always convene, for their information;

c. Require the Deputized MDDRMO to submit his explanation on his failure to submit the Report and Utilization of LDRRMF on monthly basis.

